[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0146","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0146.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0055","title":"Sun libnsl 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 操作系统的 libnsl（网络服务库）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，漏洞源于对 RPC 请求参数长度缺乏正确的边界检查。本地或远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 数据包触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获得系统的 root 权限，完全控制受影响主机。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 2.x 系列版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0055"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-05-14T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.320","remediation":"立即为 Sun Solaris 安装 Sun Security Bulletin #00172 对应补丁，为 AIX 系统安装 APAR IX80543 修复程序。如无法立即打补丁，可通过限制本地用户登录、移除不可信用户访问权限、对关键系统启用强制访问控制机制（如 SELinux）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/172","http://www-1.ibm.com/support/search.wss?rs=0&q=IX80543&apar=only"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0146.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0272","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0272.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0126","title":"SGI IRIX xterm 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 及 Solaris 5.5.1 X11R6.3 系统中 xterm 终端模拟器与 Xaw 部件库存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 xterm 的 `-xrm` 参数传递超长资源字符串触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用后可获得目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞要求攻击者拥有本地账号，攻击复杂度较低，影响 SGI IRIX 和 Solaris 等 UNIX 系统的 X11R6.3 环境。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0126"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-05-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.733","remediation":"移除 xterm 的 SUID 权限位：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/xterm`，防止本地用户通过 `-xrm` 参数以 root 权限执行任意代码。同时升级 Solaris 至 5.5.1 以上补丁版本，或从 IRIX 厂商处获取 xterm 安全修补程序。如不使用 Xaw 库程序，建议将其一并移除或降权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-010.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/338","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0126.json","ht