T00:00:00Z","references":["http://seclists.org/bugtraq/1997/May/191","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19267","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0108","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0108.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83064/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0828884e-fed7-43ba-9578-192236803d75.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e7bd3e92452a8dc8da42d94ae3ba208936d5a5b9/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0247.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0398","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0398.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0212","title":"Sun Solaris rpc.mountd 错误信息泄露漏洞","description":"Solaris/SunOS 系统中 RPC 服务 rpc.mountd 存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该服务返回详细错误信息，从而枚举服务器上的文件系统结构和文件是否存在。该漏洞影响 Solaris 及 SunOS 多个版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，为后续攻击收集目标信息。官方已发布安全补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0212"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.403","remediation":"安装 Sun Security Bulletin #168 (1998年发布) 对应的操作系统补丁，更新至已修复该问题的 Solaris 版本。如无法打补丁，可在 /etc/hosts.deny 中添加 \"mountd: ALL\" 并用 /etc/hosts.allow 按需放行可信主机，同时在防火墙上限制对 rpc.mountd (端口 2049 及 rpcbind 端口 111) 的访问。若不需要 NFS 服务，可停止并禁用 mountd 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/168","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-048.shtml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0398.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0170","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0170.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0069","title":"Sun Solaris ufsdump/ufsrestore 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 系统中的 ufsdump/ufsrestore 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，拥有本地访问权限的攻击者可通过向该工具传递特制参数触发溢出，覆盖内存数据，进而实现权限提升或以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，CVSS 评分 8.4，危害等级高危，需系统本地账号方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0069"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.363","remediation":"升级 Solaris 系统至 Solaris 8 及以上版本，或安装 Sun 官方补丁 106880-01 (SPARC) / 106881-01 (x86)。临时缓解措施：限制 ufsdump/ufsrestore 的 setuid 权限，仅授权管理用户执行文件系统备份操作。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/169","http://www.osvdb.org/8158","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19534","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0069","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f06304a9243ce013bfbf7cea427539f6409c0a05/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0069.md","https://github.com/krafthack-by-techday/Night-s-watch/blob/30ae1bcc335306fe4c5507b2c629cae4932e515e/cve/nvd/CVE-1999-0069_0f0c3530-7572-4860-a943-991d78115c24","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xqg2-r5rv-62x6/GHSA-xqg2-r5rv-62x6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0170.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0170.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0170.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0373","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0373.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0190","title":"Sun Solaris rpcbind 任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统的 rpcbind 服务存在任意文件写入漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统的 rpcbind 服务发送特制 RPC 请求，利用符号链接或文件路径遍历等方式覆盖系统任意文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议及时安装对应安全补丁进行修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0190"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:49.320","remediation":"立即应用 Sun Security Bulletin #167 提供的补丁程序，或升级到 Solaris 7 及以上版本。作为临时缓解措施，在 /etc/hosts.deny 中添加 ALL:ALL 限制 rpcbind 访问，并在防火墙上仅允许受信任网络访问 rpcbind 端口 111/TCP 和 111/UDP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/167"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0373.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0046","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0046.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0011","title":"ISC BIND 4.9/8 CNAME及区域传输拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 4.9 和 BIND 8 版本的域名解析服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者通过发送特制的 CNAME 资源记录或利用不规范的区域传输（Zone Transfer）请求，可导致目标 BIND 服务进程崩溃或资源耗尽，停止响应正常的域名解析请求。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 DNS 服务器，在无需认证的条件下即可触发，对网络基础设施的可用性构成直接威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0011"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.490","remediation":"立即升级 ISC BIND 至 8.2 及以上版本，推荐直接迁移至 BIND 9.x 系列。在 named.conf 中配置 allow-transfer 仅允许受信从服务器（如 allow-transfer { 192.168.1.2; };），并在面向不可信网络的接口上通过 allow-query 和 allow-recursion 限制查询来源。如无法立即升级，可在边界防火墙阻断外部对 TCP 53 端口的区域传输请求，并限制 UDP 53 的异常 CNAME 查询流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/180","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9808-083"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0046.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0044","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0044.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0010","title":"ISC BIND 4.9/8 DNS Message 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 4.9 及 8 版本中的 DNS 消息处理组件存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制的恶意 DNS 查询消息，利用消息解析过程中的缺陷触发服务崩溃，导致 DNS 服务不可用。该漏洞影响大量使用上述版本 BIND 的 DNS 服务器，攻击者通过发送精心构造的 DNS 请求报文即可实施攻击，无需复杂前置条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0010"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.340","remediation":"升级至 BIND 8.2 或更高版本以修复 DNS 消息解析缺陷；BIND 4.9/8 系列已停止维护，建议迁移至 BIND 9.x 系列并升级到 ISC 发布的最新稳定版（如 9.18.x 或 9.20.x）。如暂无法升级，应在边界防火墙上限制外部 DNS 查询来源 IP 并启用递归查询访问控制列表以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9808-083"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0044.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0030","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0030.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0009","title":"ISC BIND 反向查询远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ISC BIND（Berkeley Internet Name Domain）4.9 及 8.x 版本存在反向查询缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标 DNS 服务器发送特制的反向查询请求，触发缓冲区溢出，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响运行 BIND 4.9 及 8.x 的多种操作系统平台，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商建议立即升级至不受影响的版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0009"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.137","remediation":"立即升级 BIND 至 8.2 或更高版本，或在条件允许时迁移至 BIND 9 系列（如 9.3.0+），因为 8.2 已修复逆查询缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在 named.conf 中禁用 `inverse-query` 选项以临时缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/180","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/134","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9808-083","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19112","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0009.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0009","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0009.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0009.md","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/252.txt","https://github.com/demisto/content/blob/710308a4be78e89bc993b4d594b444aeb805b7d8/Packs/McAfeeNSM/Integrations/McAfeeNSMv2/README.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-p4fw-6pfr-4xqr/GHSA-p4fw-6pfr-4xqr.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0009.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/deleted.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/B/bind_iquery.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0030.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0456","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0456.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0270","title":"SGI IRIX Performer API Search Tool 目录遍历漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统自带的 Performer API Search Tool 中的 pfdispaly.cgi 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 CGI 程序发送包含特殊路径序列（如 ../）的恶意 HTTP 请求，突破 Web 根目录限制，读取服务器上任意文件，包括 /etc/passwd 等敏感系统文件。该漏洞影响安装了 performer_tools 组件的 SGI IRIX 系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。厂商已发布安全公告建议禁用相关 CGI 脚本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0270"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.600","remediation":"建议立即升级 SGI Performer API Search Tool 至最新补丁版本，或从 Web 服务器中移除 pfdispaly.cgi 脚本。如无法升级，可在 Web 服务器配置中限制对 pfdispaly.cgi 的访问（如禁用该 CGI 执行权限、限制访问来源 IP），并部署 Web 应用防火墙拦截目录遍历攻击载荷。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-041.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/134","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/64","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/810","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0270","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/2d2ea2d13a3a7facfa195486d4f9782c62a06518/1999/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0270.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0456.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0815","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0815.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0551","title":"HP OpenMail 任意命令执行漏洞","description":"HP OpenMail 邮件系统存在安全配置缺陷，由于对打印请求的访问控制权限设置不当，拥有本地访问权限的攻击者可通过发送恶意构造的打印请求绕过安全限制，在目标系统上以 OpenMail 服务进程权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 HP OpenMail 服务器，攻击者需具备本地用户权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0551"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:37.113","remediation":"限制 HP OpenMail 打印服务仅允许受信任用户提交打印请求，在 OpenMail 配置中禁用不必要的命令执行接口，并升级到厂商修复此问题的最新版本。同时在系统层面限制 OpenMail 运行账户的最小权限，防止恶意打印请求执行任意命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9804-078"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0815.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0804","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0804.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0537","title":"Internet Explorer 及 Netscape Navigator 活动内容执行漏洞","description":"该漏洞源于网页浏览器（如 Internet Explorer 或 Netscape Navigator）的安全配置缺陷，允许网页中嵌入的 ActiveX、Java、JavaScript 等活跃内容在客户端自动执行。远程攻击者可利用此配置缺陷构造恶意网页，诱导用户访问后即可在用户浏览器上下文中执行任意脚本代码或 ActiveX 控件，导致敏感信息泄露、会话劫持或系统权限被滥用。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 及 Netscape Navigator 等主流浏览器，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0537"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.140","remediation":"建议升级至现代浏览器（如 Chrome/Firefox/Edge），这些浏览器默认启用沙盒隔离与内容安全策略。如必须使用 IE，将 Internet 安全区域中「ActiveX 控件和插件」「Java 小程序」「脚本」均设为「禁用」，并通过组策略强制推送；同时在 Web 服务器层配置 Content-Security-Policy 标头限制脚本来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0537"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0804.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0761","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0761.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0507","title":"网络设备默认口令安全漏洞","description":"路由器、防火墙或其他网络设备存在默认或可猜测口令漏洞，远程攻击者可通过暴力破解或字典攻击等方式猜测设备管理账户口令，成功登录后可获取设备控制权限，进而篡改网络配置、拦截通信流量或发起进一步攻击。该漏洞影响大量开源路由器及各类网络设备，CVSS评分7.5，危害等级高。修复方式为修改默认口令并启用账户锁定策略。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0507"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.553","remediation":"立即修改所有网络设备（路由器、防火墙等）上的默认账号口令，使用至少12位含大小写字母、数字及特殊字符的强密码。禁用不必要的默认账户（如guest/admin），配置登录失败锁定策略（连续5次失败后锁定30分钟），并定期更换口令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0507"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0761.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0442","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0442.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0257","title":"Linux Kernel IP Fragmentation Nestea 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0257 即 Nestea 变种 Teardrop IP 碎片拒绝服务攻击，攻击者向目标系统发送精心构造的、偏移量重叠的畸形 IP 分片数据包，目标系统在重组这些分片时因算法缺陷导致内存计算错误，引发系统崩溃或重启。该漏洞无需认证即可远程利用，影响 Linux Kernel 2.6.20.1 及众多早期操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0257"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.990","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.6.20.1 以上版本（如 2.6.21+），该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。无法升级时，可在 iptables 中添加规则丢弃畸形 IP 分片包：iptables -A INPUT -f -m limit --limit 100/s --limit-burst 100 -j ACCEPT 或使用防火墙过滤分片重叠的恶意数据包作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0257","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0257","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0257.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5h5w-wrfr-qmhc/GHSA-5h5w-wrfr-qmhc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/N/nestea.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0442.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0229","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0229.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0098","title":"Sendmail SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sendmail SMTP 服务在处理 HELO 命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器的 25 端口发送特制的 HELO 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用可导致任意代码执行或服务崩溃，攻击者借此可完全控制服务器或隐藏恶意活动痕迹。该漏洞影响多个版本的 Sendmail，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0098"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.903","remediation":"立即升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 或更高版本（该版本修复了 SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出问题）。SLMail 用户应升级至 3.0 及以上版本，Mercury Mail Server 用户升级至最新版本。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面限制 SMTP（TCP 25）端口仅允许可信来源访问，同时在 Sendmail 配置中限制 HELO 命令输入长度作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0098"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0229.toml"}]